59
00:02:00,599 --> 00:02:01,159
Six o'clock?

60
00:02:01,159 --> 00:02:02,000
Six o'clock.

61
00:02:04,319 --> 00:02:04,920
Then...

62
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:07,319
