112
00:04:01,240 --> 00:04:02,479
Two people per group.

113
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,319
Calculate independently.

114
00:04:03,479 --> 00:04:04,599
The error in your data

115
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,879
cannot exceed two percent.

116
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:08,240
The recording method

117
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:08,919
is right here,

118
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:10,599
