119
00:04:10,599 --> 00:04:11,599
Take a look, everyone.

120
00:04:12,599 --> 00:04:13,360
Remember,

121
00:04:13,639 --> 00:04:15,000
lacewings and ladybugs

122
00:04:15,159 --> 00:04:16,959
are natural enemies of red spider mites.

123
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:18,199
The population of these predators

124
00:04:18,199 --> 00:04:20,240
is a very important reference indicator.

125
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,639
So take this seriously.

126
00:04:21,639 --> 00:04:22,079
Okay.

127
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:23,079
Ask me anytime if you have questions.

128
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:23,600
Okay.

129
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:24,199
Okay.

130
00:04:24,199 --> 00:04:24,720
Let's get to work.

131
00:04:25,319 --> 00:04:26,120
Just get it done.

132
00:04:27,199 --> 00:04:27,959
Go, go, go.

133
00:04:28,519 --> 00:04:29,160
Let's go, Xiao Yin.

134
00:04:29,160 --> 00:04:30,040
Go, go, go.

135
00:04:30,240 --> 00:04:30,720
