164
00:05:20,040 --> 00:05:21,759
The grouper here is fresh and cheap.

165
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,839
It's still jumping around alive.

166
00:05:25,879 --> 00:05:27,839
My performance numbers are here.

167
00:05:42,639 --> 00:05:43,319
Dear,

168
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:48,240
I was at the seafood market

169
00:05:48,399 --> 00:05:49,360
