217
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:46,839
No rush, Xiao Yin.

218
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:47,480
Let's count slowly.

219
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:48,480
Let's have some patience.

220
00:07:53,759 --> 00:07:54,279
Xiao Yin,

221
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:55,800
Professor Wang asked us

222
00:07:55,800 --> 00:07:57,680
