232
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,399
Counting natural predators is also a control variable.

233
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:16,519
That's the only way to compare the new species' effectiveness.

234
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:17,639
I heard

235
00:08:17,879 --> 00:08:19,319
that the lab results this time,

236
00:08:19,319 --> 00:08:20,439
and the data, are very good.

237
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,319
Basically, without intervention,

238
00:08:22,519 --> 00:08:23,519
red spiders per hundred leaves

239
00:08:23,519 --> 00:08:24,319
