240
00:08:24,319 --> 00:08:25,199
It doesn't affect the fruiting.

241
00:08:27,439 --> 00:08:29,600
I saw the lab's control data too.

242
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:29,920
But,

243
00:08:29,920 --> 00:08:31,600
one, fifty, or five hundred,

244
00:08:31,600 --> 00:08:32,639
