245
00:08:32,639 --> 00:08:33,279
They're all scary!

246
00:08:33,639 --> 00:08:34,840
I'm just afraid of bugs.

247
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,320
What should I do?

248
00:08:38,519 --> 00:08:39,120
I lost count.

249
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:40,399
Twenty-five or twenty-six?

250
00:08:40,639 --> 00:08:41,399
Twenty-seven.

251
00:08:41,399 --> 00:08:43,360
