262
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,879
Alright, alright, stop arguing.

263
00:09:10,679 --> 00:09:12,080
Just calculate it again.

264
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:12,840
Hurry up, hurry up, again.

265
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,240
Recalculate.

266
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,679
Calculate it again.

267
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:16,320
Hurry up, hurry up.

268
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:18,200
Fang'er.

269
00:09:19,120 --> 00:09:21,440
You really are the chosen agronomist.

270
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:27,639
I'm not eating, I'm not eating.

271
00:09:27,639 --> 00:09:28,600
Eat it. It's fresh. It's so sweet.

272
00:09:28,600 --> 00:09:29,200
I won't eat it.

273
00:09:29,399 --> 00:09:29,919
Have a bite.

274
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,120
These past few days,

275
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:37,039
I've been thinking,

276
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:39,120
