277
00:09:39,600 --> 00:09:40,879
I have to find someone she can rely on.

278
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:42,360
Ruirui, tell me,

279
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,480
after I'm gone,

280
00:09:45,159 --> 00:09:46,360
