854
00:30:07,480 --> 00:30:08,079
Find me?

855
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:19,079
Uncle

856
00:30:20,200 --> 00:30:20,720
Where is Wei Mingtian?

857
00:30:20,880 --> 00:30:21,920
Secretary Sun, what brings you here?

858
00:30:21,920 --> 00:30:22,599
Where is Wei Mingtian?

859
00:30:23,079 --> 00:30:23,799
He just left.

860
00:30:23,799 --> 00:30:25,240
Did you not see his car?

861
00:30:36,039 --> 00:30:36,720
I'm a step too late.

862
00:30:37,759 --> 00:30:38,240
As for me,

863
00:30:38,480 --> 00:30:40,440
I also walked out of Huangyanshan step by step.

864
00:30:40,680 --> 00:30:41,079
Studying,

865
00:30:41,480 --> 00:30:42,359
and then repaying my hometown.

866
00:30:42,880 --> 00:30:43,799
I want to invite you back

867
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:45,839
to be our Tourism Promotion Ambassador.

868
00:30:47,119 --> 00:30:48,559
The money might not be that much,

869
00:30:48,759 --> 00:30:50,359
but you can drive the development of our hometown.

870
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:51,880
At the same time,

871
00:30:52,319 --> 00:30:53,640
I will help you find a legal consultant

872
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:55,319
to move forward with the contract termination.

873
00:30:55,559 --> 00:30:57,359
Even if you want to continue your studies,

874
00:30:57,400 --> 00:30:58,079
that's no problem.

875
00:30:58,839 --> 00:31:00,279
And I will work on convincing your parents.

876
00:31:00,920 --> 00:31:01,960
You mean

877
00:31:02,559 --> 00:31:03,680
I can represent my hometown?

878
00:31:04,880 --> 00:31:05,759
Is my ability enough?

879
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:07,839
You have to reach for it to see if you're enough.

880
00:31:08,119 --> 00:31:08,640
Besides,

881
00:31:08,799 --> 00:31:09,880
you're even less skilled at being a star,

882
00:31:09,880 --> 00:31:11,200
but haven't you persisted until now?

883
00:31:12,119 --> 00:31:12,640
Although

884
00:31:12,960 --> 00:31:14,920
I think the best timing has already passed,

885
00:31:15,400 --> 00:31:15,920
but

886
00:31:15,920 --> 00:31:17,079
it shouldn't be too late.

887
00:31:18,519 --> 00:31:18,839
How about this,

888
00:31:19,559 --> 00:31:20,279
this is my business card.

889
00:31:21,039 --> 00:31:21,720
Think about it first.

890
00:31:22,039 --> 00:31:22,920
If you have any questions,

891
00:31:22,920 --> 00:31:24,039
contact me anytime.

892
00:31:24,960 --> 00:31:25,319
Okay?

893
00:31:26,000 --> 00:31:26,680
Then you get back to what you were doing.

894
00:31:27,160 --> 00:31:27,759
I'll be going then.

895
00:31:28,119 --> 00:31:28,400
I'm off.

896
00:31:28,400 --> 00:31:29,000
Goodbye, Chief.

897
00:31:29,200 --> 00:31:29,559
Bye-bye.

898
00:31:42,200 --> 00:31:42,680
Guifang.

899
00:31:54,680 --> 00:31:55,279
What's wrong?

900
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:56,880
You look like you have something on your mind.

901
00:31:57,160 --> 00:31:59,000
This data is just very strange.

902
00:31:59,160 --> 00:32:00,880
The more I think about it, the more I feel there's a problem.

903
00:32:07,000 --> 00:32:07,680
What's wrong with you?

904
00:32:08,319 --> 00:32:09,119
You look like

905
00:32:09,319 --> 00:32:10,119
you have something on your mind too.

906
00:32:10,599 --> 00:32:11,079
I...

907
00:32:14,039 --> 00:32:14,559
I'm fine.

908
00:32:15,279 --> 00:32:16,039
I just...

909
00:32:16,839 --> 00:32:17,440
got tired from running.

910
00:32:18,920 --> 00:32:19,519
Tired from running.

911
00:32:21,240 --> 00:32:22,400
Then shouldn't you go easy on me?

912
00:32:22,640 --> 00:32:23,480
Who's going easy on you?

913
00:32:23,680 --> 00:32:24,039
Tian'er.

914
00:32:24,359 --> 00:32:25,000
I'm not running anymore.

915
00:32:26,319 --> 00:32:27,119
You reminded me.

916
00:32:27,359 --> 00:32:28,319
I should run two more laps.

917
00:32:29,640 --> 00:32:30,240
Still running?

918
00:32:30,960 --> 00:32:31,880
Chat with my mom some more.

919
00:32:31,880 --> 00:32:32,480
It's okay, it's okay.

920
00:32:32,880 --> 00:32:34,000
Young people really have vitality.

921
00:32:35,039 --> 00:32:35,720
Guifang.

922
00:32:36,359 --> 00:32:37,359
You're already in Hainan.

923
00:32:37,359 --> 00:32:38,640
Why don't you go play by the seaside?

924
00:32:38,880 --> 00:32:39,839
I want to too.

925
00:32:40,039 --> 00:32:42,000
But it feels like something is weighing on my heart.

926
00:32:42,119 --> 00:32:43,079
Everyone comes out to play,

927
00:32:43,079 --> 00:32:43,960
but you... well...

928
00:32:44,720 --> 00:32:45,880
My body is at the seaside,

929
00:32:45,880 --> 00:32:46,960
but my heart is in the fields.

930
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:49,079
You said the first day was normal.

931
00:32:49,359 --> 00:32:50,640
But things got weird on the second day.

932
00:32:50,960 --> 00:32:51,960
There wasn't a single bug.

933
00:32:52,240 --> 00:32:53,720
Then on the third day, it went crazy.

934
00:32:53,720 --> 00:32:54,680
Bugs were flying everywhere.

935
00:32:55,039 --> 00:32:55,640
Bugs.

936
00:32:55,880 --> 00:32:57,319
Is it possible someone lured them here?

937
00:32:58,559 --> 00:32:59,720
You know, on the second day...

938
00:33:00,640 --> 00:33:02,720
Wasn't that the day I asked A Fu to kill the bugs?

939
00:33:04,960 --> 00:33:05,920
On the third day...

940
00:33:06,400 --> 00:33:08,160
A Fu looked so anxious.

941
00:33:08,519 --> 00:33:10,079
Sabotaging someone's test field...

942
00:33:10,079 --> 00:33:11,240
It's not impossible.

943
00:33:11,640 --> 00:33:13,759
How could he destroy someone's research?

944
00:33:15,799 --> 00:33:16,359
Wait a minute.

945
00:33:16,880 --> 00:33:19,079
It seems I'm the one to blame for all this.

946
00:33:19,440 --> 00:33:19,960
I'm done for.

947
00:33:20,160 --> 00:33:20,680
Auntie.

948
00:33:21,359 --> 00:33:21,960
You must be tired.

949
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:22,759
Let me help you.

950
00:33:22,880 --> 00:33:23,680
Let me massage your shoulders.

951
00:33:23,720 --> 00:33:24,680
I... I'm not tired. I'm not tired.

952
00:33:24,799 --> 00:33:25,680
Then have some water.

953
00:33:25,799 --> 00:33:26,440
You must be hungry.

954
00:33:26,440 --> 00:33:28,240
I... I'll go order you some food.

955
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:29,519
I'm not hungry.

956
00:33:33,279 --> 00:33:33,839
How wonderful.

957
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:35,400
So diligent and sensible.

958
00:33:39,839 --> 00:33:42,000
You... you just keep researching.

959
00:33:46,960 --> 00:33:47,319
Buddy.

960
00:33:47,960 --> 00:33:48,759
Help me salvage this.

961
00:33:49,319 --> 00:33:50,240
Fix it up nicely.

962
00:33:53,319 --> 00:33:53,880
Oh my god.

963
00:34:12,960 --> 00:34:14,280
Xiao Yin's gonna kill me if she sees this.

964
00:34:15,079 --> 00:34:16,400
Are you crazy, Kong Xiaocan?

965
00:34:20,840 --> 00:34:21,400
Dad, Mom.

966
00:34:21,599 --> 00:34:22,480
What are you doing here?

967
00:34:22,480 --> 00:34:23,559
My dear daughter.

968
00:34:23,760 --> 00:34:24,960
Why is your room such a mess?

969
00:34:25,119 --> 00:34:26,440
It looks like a boys' dorm.

970
00:34:26,559 --> 00:34:27,440
Dad, stop cleaning.

971
00:34:27,440 --> 00:34:28,440
I can clean it myself.

972
00:34:28,440 --> 00:34:29,239
Let me do it.

973
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:30,480
I've got it, I've got it. It's fine.

974
00:34:30,480 --> 00:34:31,400
Here, let me.

975
00:34:39,960 --> 00:34:41,800
You're not studying properly at school again, are you?

976
00:34:43,000 --> 00:34:45,000
Messing around with this sewing nonsense all day.

977
00:34:45,000 --> 00:34:46,519
What are you doing? You want to be a tailor?

978
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:47,719
I just...

979
00:34:47,880 --> 00:34:48,719
What's wrong with it?

980
00:34:48,800 --> 00:34:50,480
Can't you just leave me alone?

981
00:34:50,559 --> 00:34:52,039
If I don't, you'll turn the house upside down.

982
00:34:52,400 --> 00:34:54,000
I'm worried this will get in the way of your studies.

983
00:34:54,159 --> 00:34:56,440
I... I haven't let it affect my studies.

984
00:34:56,440 --> 00:34:57,679
You haven't let it affect your studies?

985
00:34:57,679 --> 00:34:58,800
You don't feel it right now.

986
00:34:59,079 --> 00:35:00,199
But when your grades drop later on,

987
00:35:00,199 --> 00:35:01,199
you'll be the one crying.

988
00:35:01,519 --> 00:35:03,039
No, Mom, what are you doing?

989
00:35:03,039 --> 00:35:04,679
I just like doing this stuff.

990
00:35:04,679 --> 00:35:05,280
You like it?

991
00:35:05,280 --> 00:35:05,519
Yes.

992
00:35:05,639 --> 00:35:07,159
You like everything except studying.

993
00:35:08,039 --> 00:35:09,199
If you keep messing with this junk,

994
00:35:09,400 --> 00:35:10,639
I'll throw it all out the window.

995
00:35:11,320 --> 00:35:12,480
What gives you the right to throw my stuff?

996
00:35:12,480 --> 00:35:13,320
This is my own stuff.

997
00:35:13,320 --> 00:35:14,159
Why can't I throw it?

998
00:35:14,280 --> 00:35:14,840
Shut up.

999
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:18,360
Xiao Yin.

1000
00:35:20,079 --> 00:35:21,119
Hello, Auntie. Hello, Uncle.

1001
00:35:21,199 --> 00:35:21,639
You're here.

1002
00:35:22,159 --> 00:35:22,880
Look at this photo.

1003
00:35:23,119 --> 00:35:24,039
How is it? Do you like it?

1004
00:35:24,679 --> 00:35:25,360
I don't like it.

1005
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,239
It's useless even if you like it.

1006
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:29,280
Am I being too nice to you?

1007
00:35:29,599 --> 00:35:31,039
Don't, don't, don't. Don't be so angry.

1008
00:35:32,519 --> 00:35:33,079
What's wrong, Uncle?

1009
00:35:33,239 --> 00:35:34,360
I'm not talking to you, Li Wai.

1010
00:35:34,519 --> 00:35:35,519
It's between the two of them.

1011
00:35:38,519 --> 00:35:38,960
Turn around.

1012
00:35:42,679 --> 00:35:43,239
Chen Xiaoyin.

1013
00:35:43,519 --> 00:35:44,079
Your classmate is here.

1014
00:35:44,079 --> 00:35:45,119
I'm giving you some face today.

1015
00:35:46,239 --> 00:35:47,400
If you just behave yourself,

1016
00:35:47,639 --> 00:35:48,480
get good grades,

1017
00:35:48,760 --> 00:35:49,800
and find a good job later,

1018
00:35:50,519 --> 00:35:51,519
would Mom bother you about this?

1019
00:35:52,079 --> 00:35:53,400
Then you can pedal that sewing machine until it takes off.

1020
00:35:53,400 --> 00:35:54,119
Mom won't say a word.

1021
00:35:54,599 --> 00:35:55,960
You can even make a nice outfit for Mom.

1022
00:35:56,599 --> 00:35:57,000
Right?

1023
00:35:57,960 --> 00:35:58,880
But right now,

1024
00:35:59,280 --> 00:36:00,679
your main priority is studying.

1025
00:36:01,800 --> 00:36:03,360
Put your hobbies on the back burner for now.

1026
00:36:04,000 --> 00:36:04,320
Right.

1027
00:36:05,280 --> 00:36:05,599
Auntie.

1028
00:36:05,880 --> 00:36:06,480
You're right.

1029
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:08,039
Listen to your classmate's advice.

1030
00:36:08,119 --> 00:36:08,800
But only half right.

1031
00:36:09,960 --> 00:36:10,639
Studying,

1032
00:36:10,800 --> 00:36:11,440
is certainly important,

1033
00:36:11,880 --> 00:36:12,719
but I think,

1034
00:36:13,159 --> 00:36:14,519
at our age right now,

1035
00:36:14,840 --> 00:36:16,039
having a hobby that

1036
00:36:16,039 --> 00:36:17,159
we truly love is more important.

1037
00:36:18,400 --> 00:36:19,199
Uncle, have some water.

1038
00:36:20,800 --> 00:36:21,239
I think,

1039
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:22,760
while we're young,

1040
00:36:23,079 --> 00:36:24,159
we should try out more of

1041
00:36:24,159 --> 00:36:25,559
the things we truly love.

1042
00:36:25,840 --> 00:36:27,360
If we wait until we're your and Uncle's age,

1043
00:36:27,360 --> 00:36:28,880
it might be too late to try.

1044
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:29,559
Drink a little less.

1045
00:36:30,599 --> 00:36:31,920
The clothes Xiao Yin made,

1046
00:36:32,039 --> 00:36:32,559
I've seen them.

1047
00:36:32,719 --> 00:36:34,199
although there's still room for improvement, kid,

1048
00:36:34,199 --> 00:36:35,519
they're already very nice.

1049
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:38,199
Look at your uncle coughing like that.

1050
00:36:39,440 --> 00:36:40,360
Go buy him some medicine.

1051
00:36:41,960 --> 00:36:42,360
Auntie.

1052
00:36:43,159 --> 00:36:43,400
Medicine.

1053
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:44,039
You're getting older.

1054
00:36:44,039 --> 00:36:44,719
You've been through this too.

1055
00:36:44,719 --> 00:36:45,679
You surely understand what I'm saying.

1056
00:36:45,679 --> 00:36:46,039
Medicine.

1057
00:36:46,360 --> 00:36:47,039
Buy me some medicine.

1058
00:36:47,199 --> 00:36:47,639
Just something to soothe the throat.

1059
00:36:47,639 --> 00:36:48,880
Okay, okay, right away.

1060
00:36:50,519 --> 00:36:51,239
This child.

1061
00:36:52,199 --> 00:36:52,840
Calm down.

1062
00:36:53,119 --> 00:36:53,960
You shut up. It's no big deal.

1063
00:36:54,679 --> 00:36:55,039
Turn back around.

1064
00:36:58,800 --> 00:36:59,239
Fine.

1065
00:37:00,000 --> 00:37:01,199
You're all on the same side.

1066
00:37:01,920 --> 00:37:03,440
You're all right, and I'm the only one wrong, huh?

1067
00:37:09,400 --> 00:37:09,840
Chen Xiaoyin

1068
00:37:13,280 --> 00:37:14,280
You can do it

1069
00:37:15,760 --> 00:37:16,239
But

1070
00:37:16,519 --> 00:37:18,079
if this affects your grades

1071
00:37:19,079 --> 00:37:20,800
I'll beat both you and your dad then

1072
00:37:25,280 --> 00:37:25,800
All right, all right

1073
00:37:26,280 --> 00:37:27,079
It's over, it's over

1074
00:37:27,440 --> 00:37:28,079
Hurry up and thank Mom

1075
00:37:28,800 --> 00:37:29,440
Thanks, Mom

1076
00:37:29,639 --> 00:37:30,639
Don't... don't give me that nonsense

1077
00:37:31,679 --> 00:37:33,880
I think what that kid Li Wai said

1078
00:37:34,199 --> 00:37:34,960
was pretty right

1079
00:37:35,320 --> 00:37:36,519
It's a bit like my wisdom

1080
00:37:36,960 --> 00:37:37,280
Yeah

1081
00:37:37,639 --> 00:37:38,400
Just as dim-witted

1082
00:37:39,719 --> 00:37:40,519
Your mom is funny

1083
00:37:40,599 --> 00:37:41,320
Get out of here

1084
00:37:42,079 --> 00:37:42,880
Go get some fruit for the kid

1085
00:37:43,079 --> 00:37:43,559
You got it

1086
00:37:44,599 --> 00:37:45,000
Just wait

1087
00:37:46,760 --> 00:37:47,639
Don't hold me

1088
00:37:47,760 --> 00:37:48,719
Didn't you say I was old?

1089
00:37:48,719 --> 00:37:49,280
I can walk by myself

1090
00:37:50,280 --> 00:37:51,320
Where do you look old?

1091
00:38:10,079 --> 00:38:10,519
Li Wai

1092
00:38:11,000 --> 00:38:12,639
Send me those photos

1093
00:38:12,639 --> 00:38:13,440
you secretly took of me just now.

1094
00:38:18,400 --> 00:38:19,599
I did it, okay?

1095
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:20,880
It was all me.

1096
00:38:21,039 --> 00:38:21,800
Please.

1097
00:38:21,800 --> 00:38:22,440
First of all,

1098
00:38:22,679 --> 00:38:24,480
I am a higher civilization.

1099
00:38:24,719 --> 00:38:25,280
Secondly,

1100
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:27,480
I am a higher civilization.

1101
00:38:27,480 --> 00:38:29,199
Look at how tortured I am now.

1102
00:38:29,320 --> 00:38:30,639
I can't even speak clearly anymore.

1103
00:38:30,800 --> 00:38:31,400
I'm telling you,

1104
00:38:31,400 --> 00:38:32,360
if I get optimized,

1105
00:38:32,480 --> 00:38:33,519
it won't end well for you guys.

1106
00:38:34,119 --> 00:38:35,239
You should have been optimized ages ago.

1107
00:38:37,159 --> 00:38:38,239
It feels so awful.

1108
00:38:38,440 --> 00:38:39,000
I just feel like...

1109
00:38:39,199 --> 00:38:40,039
my eyes...

1110
00:38:40,199 --> 00:38:41,639
keep wanting to leak water.

1111
00:38:41,639 --> 00:38:42,519
Alright, stop being sad.

1112
00:38:42,519 --> 00:38:43,159
Crying is useless.

1113
00:38:43,159 --> 00:38:44,320
Crying won't make her soft-hearted anyway.

1114
00:38:45,480 --> 00:38:45,840
I...

1115
00:38:46,199 --> 00:38:48,519
My chest, from last night until now,

1116
00:38:48,679 --> 00:38:50,199
has been hurting constantly.

1117
00:38:50,639 --> 00:38:51,199
Are you sure

1118
00:38:51,199 --> 00:38:52,960
you still want to stay with this woman?

1119
00:38:53,559 --> 00:38:54,679
I've set my heart on her for this lifetime.

1120
00:38:54,679 --> 00:38:55,239
So what?

1121
00:38:56,559 --> 00:38:57,000
Humans...

1122
00:38:57,440 --> 00:38:58,440
are so complex.

1123
00:39:00,760 --> 00:39:01,679
Why?

1124
00:39:01,679 --> 00:39:02,920
I don't want to.

1125
00:39:03,360 --> 00:39:04,480
Alright, alright, alright.

1126
00:39:04,480 --> 00:39:05,199
Stop crying.

1127
00:39:06,880 --> 00:39:07,519
I promise you,

1128
00:39:08,239 --> 00:39:08,599
from now on,

1129
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:09,760
I won't torture you anymore.

1130
00:39:10,039 --> 00:39:10,639
You swear.

1131
00:39:11,119 --> 00:39:11,840
I swear.

1132
00:39:13,159 --> 00:39:13,599
However,

1133
00:39:14,000 --> 00:39:16,280
in the future, create your own performance stats.

1134
00:39:16,480 --> 00:39:18,159
Don't ruin others' experimental results anymore.

1135
00:39:18,159 --> 00:39:18,719
Do you hear me?

